title: Deltaisos for Fedora 13 -> Fedora 14 Beta x86_64
description:
Deltaisos to generate the entire Fedora 14 Beta x86_64 install disc set. First apply Fedora-13_14-Beta-x86_64-DVD.diso to the F13 Final x86_64 DVD ISO to generate the F14 Beta x86_64 DVD ISO.  The other deltaisos can then be applied to the new DVD image to generate any of the other new install images (CD and netinst).

Instructions at https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Delta_ISOs
